Hello!

   This changeset merges new block allocator for reiserfs and adds
   one more tail policy for shorter tails. New block allocator contains code
   from Alexander Zarochencev, Jeff Mahoney and Oleg Drokin. Please apply.

   You can get it from bk://thebsh.namesys.com/bk/reiser3-linux-2.5


